        {
          "username": "Intrepid Adventurer",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "106962465705044053239",
          "user_review_count": 26,
          "user_photo_count": 8,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyW53UzeRIiVMbhbDeCfDdUnfi4o0Fi_i8jdYJCnyWapiSYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "LAME-UNPROFESSIONAL-SHAMEFUL\n\nReview of Family Health Center of Harlem:  Unprofessional and Lacking Empathy\n\nMy experience with the Family Health Center of Harlem has been extremely disappointing. I initially had a phone interview with a mental health specialist, after which I was passed on to a supposed mental health professional named Marsha, who began my evaluation. We were scheduled to have our second session today. Instead, after two weeks of no therapy (that is their schedule, not mine), I was abruptly informed that \u201cit would be in my best interest if I provide you with a referral\u201d, essentially, that they would not be providing me with mental health services.\n\nOnly now, on the day of the session, was I told that she had discussed my case with her supervisor and they made this decision. Why wait two weeks to communicate something so important? Why waste my time and allow me to prepare for a session that was never going to happen?\n(In total, it has been almost two months since I started this process, only to end up back on the street again. No wonder so many people in NYC are struggling with their mental health and left without proper care.)\n\nThis behavior is: unprofessional, inconsiderate, and shows a clear lack of empathy. I do not need a referral. I need a provider who actually cares about their patients and treats their time and mental health with respect. My experience here was deeply disappointing and felt dismissive rather than supportive.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJMFQzbEZXbmhhVEVWWllVTk9PRU5hUVRsSVpWRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xed6584ad8e56a218!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjI0T3lFWnhaTEVZYUNOOENaQTlIZVE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "6 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-12-10T14:25:13+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "Marcus Marcus",
