          "description": "Front desk attendants always have an attitude and don\u2019t like assisting customers . Very unprofessional. They will eat and be on their phones but won\u2019t provide exceptional service . They also drilled in my mouth without verifying my insurance and immediately stopped bc it wasn\u2019t approved which cause me pain when my mouth want bothering me before . I was going to leave a good review for my actual dentist but because of the unprofessionalism I can\u2019t .",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kSFRWcENaVGw1TlZONVpsVlhNV0pvTFhaTFprRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xed6584ad8e56a218!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmdHTVpCZTl5NVN5ZlVXMWJoLXZLZkE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "3 months ago",
