          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqCrhCKiF4Hph2enPEkeCfBeTDbBYIJU3XkRf_T24ZrdaxycZa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I met with Grace, one of the physician's assistants, for a check-up and to refill some prescriptions and she was incredible. The office was very busy today, yet she listened to everything I had to say, was very responsive, and incredibly efficient. I never felt like I was holding her up or taking too long; it was a very natural conversation. I have been to MDs who did not have the bedside manner and understanding that Grace did!",
