          "description": "Once you get past the hurdle of the referral/intake, it's just fine.\nMost of the communications with the physicians can be done via the MyChart app (appointments, prescription questions, etc). Not so much with any caseworkers or therapists, though. I highly recommend you get the app: MyChart by Epic\nappsto.re/us/in20w.i\n\nThey have super late hours. This is a HUGE plus for me. Where else can you make an 8PM appointment on a weekend???\n\nThe facilities are always clean. Especially as late as I come in. Because I've seen some messy adults with their even messier kids wreck the waiting room on my earlier visits. It's only as good as you treat it people...\n\nAnd the free King-sized condoms don't hurt either. Well... I'm not even going to finish that thought.",
